node.text:
Life’s too short!
So spend it with people who make you laugh & feel loved. 
Take the risk & go after what you want.
Control what you can, let go of what you can’t! 
Believe everything happens for a reason and thank the universe everyday for what you have in this moment, because ‘Now’ is the only moment that ever exists.
🌞😊🌸🏝⛰💛💗
